wiki.summary: "Love You Different" is the thirteenth track off Justin Bieber's studio album "Justice". The lyrics to "Love You Different" are pretty straightforward, message-wise, promising over and over, "I will love you different just the way you are." The song doesn't name Justin Bieber's wife, Hailey Bieber, by name — but there's no question she's the inspiration. Referring to another track on the album, "2 Much," Bieber told Vogue, "I'm a hopeless romantic. This is one of those songs where I get to talk about how much I love my wife." Read more on Last.fm.
